metadata.name: Believe
metadata.description:
1/1 art, oil painting on canvas.
I made this painting in a year 2022. When there were so many terrible things happening around. 
And You have to believe to keep going. 
Not to stack in your fear or anger. 
And keep believing the best in people. 
Best in yourself. 
Stay kind, calm, responsive, strong. 
Whatever happens. 
3024 × 3878px 300dpi
